Maintainer: Thomas Dumond <thomas.dumond@adelaide.edu.au>
Description: Provides functions to automatically retrieve and deduplicate
    reference metadata based on saved search strings.
    Access to Web of Science and Scopus requires personal API keys,
    while PubMed can be queried without one.
